      <title>Ecopetrol狩猎加勒比海水域的海上天然气储量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/ecopetrol-hunts-for-offshore-gas-reserves-in-caribbean-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚的国有能源生产商Ecopetrol SA计划很快就开始在加勒比海水域钻探另一孔，以增加其天然气储备的下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/ecopetrol-hunts-for-offshore-gas-reserves-in-caribbean-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 18:56:25 GMT</pubDate>
